description.narrative: This activity (Seconded National Experts (SNEs)) is a component of DFID Secondees to the European Union (April 2011 to March 2015) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Multilateral organisation' and a budget of £13,543,452. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Sectors not specified. The start date is 01-04-2011 and the end date is 01-09-2016.
